# install_secrets -- local-only override for the HDA install path.
#
# Copy this file to `install_secrets` (drop the .example) and put your
# preferred install directory on a single line.  Lines starting with #
# are ignored, blank lines too.  install.sh / install.bat will use the
# first remaining line as the default install path -- you can hit Enter
# at the prompt instead of typing it every time.
#
# `install_secrets` (no .example) is gitignored.  This template is
# committed.
#
# Example:
# /Users/you/path/to/your/otls/
